 Mark Description: 
The mark consists of the following: A circle comprised of four broken lines in dark blue. Inside the circle appear four chevrons. The chevron on the left has a dark green top and light green bottom, the chevron on the right has a light green top and a dark green bottom. The chevron on the top is dark blue on the right side and light blue on the left side. The chevron on the bottom has a dark blue left side and light blue right side. The terms "HOME POINT" above "CAPITAL" all in dark blue appear below the design.


