			Company Description 


			Point Capital, Inc. operates as closed-end, non-diversified investment company. The company's investment objective is to provide current income and capital appreciation. Its investments are made principally through direct investments in prospective portfolio companies. The company was founded on Jul...
		


                Point Capital, Inc. operates as closed-end, non-diversified investment company. The company's investment objective is to provide current income and capital appreciation. Its investments are made principally through direct investments in prospective portfolio companies. The company was founded on July 13, 2010 and is headquartered in Englewood, NJ.
            




